        "reaction_type": "热解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Pyrolysis reaction",
        "description": "在固定床反应器中使用纳米MOF衍生的Y沸石催化剂，对城市塑料废物进行催化热解，生产汽油、喷气燃料和柴油。实验评估了温度（375–525°C）、沸石结晶度（0–100%）和催化剂负载量（2.5–17.5%）对液体燃料产率的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Catalytic pyrolysis of municipal plastic waste... three key parameters were selected for experimental design: temperature (375–525 ◦C), catalyst loading in the reactor (2.5–17.5 %), and support crystallinity percentage (0–100 %). Using a response surface approach, the impact of these parameters on the liquid fuel production efficiency was investigated.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Pyrolysis reaction"
      }
    ]
